      "voiceName": "Trevor Noah",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Let me tell you something: Fame won\u2019t make you happy. \n\nMost people think fame will make them happy.\n\nBut according to Arthur C. Brooks, fame often creates the opposite effect.\n\nWatch the full episode on my YouTube channel to understand the real science of happiness.\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/Trevornoah/status/2033301210787414237",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-15T21:56:00+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "trevor-noah",
      "voiceName": "Trevor Noah",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Is the life plan everyone was told wrong? \n\nGet good grades.\nGet a good job.\nBuy a house.\nThen you\u2019ll be happy. Really?\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/Trevornoah/status/2032952915678179446",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-14T22:52:00+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "trevor-noah",
      "voiceName": "Trevor Noah",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "That is how I became a soccer fan... Anyone else?\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/Trevornoah/status/2032574421706354838",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-13T21:48:00+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "trevor-noah",
      "voiceName": "Trevor Noah",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Did Disney lie to us?\n\nWe grew up believing the good guy always wins. Turns out\u2026 the real world doesn\u2019t work like that.\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/Trevornoah/status/2032192406536270127",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-12T20:30:00+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "trevor-noah",
      "voiceName": "Trevor Noah",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Are we arguing about the wrong things?\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/Trevornoah/status/2031930541193515399",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-12T03:09:27+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "trevor-noah",
      "voiceName": "Trevor Noah",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Remember when COVID hit? Turns out we got exactly what we wished for.\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/Trevornoah/status/2031575114870042644",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-11T03:37:06+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "trevor-noah",
      "voiceName": "Trevor Noah",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "The day I crossed the Mexican border\u2026 NO PASSPORT!\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/Trevornoah/status/2031311698871857441",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-10T10:10:23+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "trevor-noah",
      "voiceName": "Trevor Noah",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "What if your boss isn\u2019t the one evaluating you anymore? What if an algorithm is?\n\nWatch the full conversation here: piped.video/MGaTvdIY_rs\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/Trevornoah/status/2030387259930038618",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-07T20:57:00+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "trevor-noah",
      "voiceName": "Trevor Noah",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "This isn\u2019t about left vs right. \n\nIt\u2019s about understanding how belief, identity, and power intersect in modern politics.\n\nWatch the full episode of What Now? for the full conversation on my YouTube channel.\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/Trevornoah/status/2030024117131300870",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-06T20:54:00+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
